birthday recap🧁 key takeaway: blessed and highly favored✨

Blessed and highly favored may be an understatement because my tribe is untouchable. Every year I’m reminded how lucky I am to have my support system. Y’all always show up and show out for me and for that I am grateful. Thank you to everyone who showed up to celebrate my day and thank you for the continuous birthday love🎂

#ariesseason

Thank you for having me @spelman_college 🩵 I can officially add “emcee” to my resume🎙️

Recently, @spotify hosted its first ever NextGen Creator Day at Spelman College and I had the honor of emceeing the event. Shoutout to all of the people behind the scenes who made this event come to life✨THIS is what I live for and I hope the resources given to Spelman College are enough to inspire the next generation of students aspiring to work in the audio industry.

And to the girl who said she listens to the @keepitcutepod, thank you🫶🏾People like you keep me going!
